Package: BioLizardStyleR
Type: Package
Title: MAKING GGPLOT GRAPHICS IN BIOLIZARD STYLE
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Robbe Neirynck
Description: The BioLizardStyleR package offers tools to craft ggplot2 visualizations 
    in the distinct BioLizard style. It features an integrated font installer, a dedicated 
    ggplot2 theme function, a collection of custom color functions, and a function for 
    appending a Biolizard footer and exporting the resultant graph.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Imports: 
    colorspace,
    extrafont,
    ggplot2


